  "remarks": "Member of the Rajah Solaiman Movement (QDe.128). Father's name is\nAmorsolo Jarabata Pareja. Mother's name is Leonila Cambaya Rosalejos. Review pursuant to\nSecurity Council resolution 1822 (2008) was concluded on 13 May 2010. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2610 (2021) was concluded on 30 October 2023.  INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
